$ 73,500,000 CRITICAL RESPONSE Section::::Critical response .
On Rotten Tomatoes , the films received 99 % , 97 % , and 67 % scores respectively .
Metacritic , based on its ratings for each film ( 100 % , 90 % , 60 % ) , lists the series as receiving " Universal Acclaim " with its 83 % average .
The films appear in many " Top 10 " film lists , such as the , IMDb top 250 , Time magazine 's All - Time 100 Movies , and James Berardinelli 's Top 100 . !
