CinemaScore ACCOLADES
Section::::Accolades .
The three films together were nominated for a total of 29 Academy Awards , of which they won nine .
For the Best Supporting Actor award , both The Godfather and The Godfather Part II had three actors nominated for the award , which is a rare feat .
Both The Godfather and The Godfather Part II won the award for Best Picture in their respective years .
The Godfather Part II won the most Academy Awards with six to its credit .
The Godfather Part III was nominated for seven Oscars , but won none .
